{"tid":124782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"女友叫我戒煙但係我完全戒唔甩 有無方法","createTime":"2017-02-18T02:01:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T11:53:12.000Z","uid":55137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4d98104bf8937454b813390d05dedbb98e898458","tid":124782,"uid":55137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:01:04.000Z","msg":"試過食薄荷糖 香口膠都係。都係唔得 求方法"},{"pid":"0afcfd918d231e8ce93c1a3b8ddb7b20ffbc07f4","tid":124782,"uid":27919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:21:49.000Z","msg":"戒煙貼+ 香口膠<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔洗一黎就要完全戒晒一枝都唔食得<br />\n<br />\n你貼住patch 有時癮好大都可以食枝煙<br />\n你自己慢慢減少到最後唔洗食咁解"},{"pid":"03aed24cbc79279ceae2f5244d137e1d033f7f5c","tid":124782,"uid":64270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:25:22.000Z","msg":"食左6年 岩岩戒左幾個禮拜<br />\n有時會好想食番 跟住我同自己講 我一食嘅話 就停唔到 就會一直食落去 之前戒落個啲就白費左心機"},{"pid":"1adfde2acc369e9b280f7f8bda4a515a83a02f28","tid":124782,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:05:34.000Z","msg":"飛左條女, 你唔好害佢"},{"pid":"3a184e630d1baff87ac95e0198e0b4b7b6f77426","tid":124782,"uid":30991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:09:43.000Z","msg":"樓主加油 我都想戒"},{"pid":"8af97269726cc85dbfbff9a4d2361f7a5e380aa7","tid":124782,"uid":18547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:13:30.000Z","msg":"參考逃學威龍嘅達叔"},{"pid":"9d64e185f8031daf98a53743e448b3c4232bb3c5","tid":124782,"uid":60980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:13:39.000Z","msg":"唔好買"},{"pid":"bf703319c08830c744895b3aabe9fe78a2d417dc","tid":124782,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:15:56.000Z","msg":"迫佢吸埋咪得"},{"pid":"e6236052cd6ebc4c78b70d3ca34c578532618007","tid":124782,"uid":36969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:16:34.000Z","msg":"戒左條女佢"},{"pid":"4b1fec0c4b9e1b89431afd754bfd5c3f8c7cd78b","tid":124782,"uid":44071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:17:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食左6年 岩岩戒左幾個禮拜<br />\n有時會好想食番 跟住我同自己講 我一食嘅話 就停唔到 就會一直食落去 之前戒落個啲就白費左心機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲係危險期<br />\n身癮已戒，但心癮未除<br />\n呢個時候心思思種感覺最危險<br />\n萬一軟弱，諗住食翻一支唔緊要，可以控制到，就會前功盡廢<br />\n又要重新經過戒身癮既痛苦過程<br />\n千萬小心保持警戒"},{"pid":"577f21c7b19175666379c6e2f4cda9a3b36d62ce","tid":124782,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:19:20.000Z","msg":"咬樹枝"},{"pid":"62c36aeb69c26ea167878c63cfb43c73177e4e44","tid":124782,"uid":29008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:27:08.000Z","msg":"貼足24個鐘戒煙貼，真係得"},{"pid":"27557a00317cc24800f1be065e52d336f4038537","tid":124782,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:35:10.000Z","msg":"讓條女俾唔食煙既巴打"},{"pid":"73712e04523714f8b278c6c02d617463b76b108b","tid":124782,"uid":64270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T06:51:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食左6年 岩岩戒左幾個禮拜<br />\n有時會好想食番 跟住我同自己講 我一食嘅話 就停唔到 就會一直食落去 之前戒落個啲就白費左心機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲係危險期<br />\n身癮已戒，但心癮未除<br />\n呢個時候心思思種感覺最危險<br />\n萬一軟弱，諗住食翻一支唔緊要，可以控制到，就會前功盡廢<br />\n又要重新經過戒身癮既痛苦過程<br />\n千萬小心保持警戒</blockquote><br />\n我完全明白<br />\n而家有時好頹 好唔開心都會好想食 <br />\n差少少就想沖落街開包煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa50cc1f4284982c854d640e7d8aecdfe296772a","tid":124782,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T06:52:58.000Z","msg":"飛左條女"},{"pid":"1432dec1d1410b82457c2d5ed453e34de6da5b99","tid":124782,"uid":81852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T06:55:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f1d5cac9329ac63212648190b6eb885ab8cfa10","tid":124782,"uid":75087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T06:57:45.000Z","msg":"過來食電子煙啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/103040/page/37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/103040/page/37</a>"},{"pid":"851e23dffecff8a376c480c9f5d78bfc6b7785cb","tid":124782,"uid":63760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T07:03:32.000Z","msg":"嗰口一次過擔住幾支煙<br />\n就會覺得食煙好辛苦<br />\n之後再諗你可以為咩而戒煙<br />\n<br />\n呢嗰方法係我好多同事試過又work<br />\n利申：冇食過煙"},{"pid":"6915692f012df663265dfcb3f23aee6e082064ae","tid":124782,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T07:04:59.000Z","msg":"你女友比你搞到有肺癌果時你就會肯戒架啦<br />\n人，係唔見棺材唔流眼淚架嘛 ，係咪?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"564b225f9df18dd65b76ccbef8ba3414a06b66d2","tid":124782,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T07:06:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b69897f9a8da8b2cbbff1c2e6f070abb0e756ae4","tid":124782,"uid":55137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T09:21:56.000Z","msg":"我一日食三包煙呀爸打"},{"pid":"eb160972c6fc053732308314b996cdbc7a0b198d","tid":124782,"uid":24366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T09:27:00.000Z","msg":"打電話去東華約姑娘啦<br />\n有免費藥<br />\n仲有現金卷"},{"pid":"281cd9b6c8244823d5d4f0c75e05f5bae1ad991b","tid":124782,"uid":55137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T09:30:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我一日食三包煙呀爸打</blockquote><br />\n巴"},{"pid":"e173a9b982c315ec356a7c6c4aa8854ee5140196","tid":124782,"uid":67203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T11:02:30.000Z","msg":"我有個同事迷上跑馬拉松、玩三項鐵人賽<br />\n佢練跑既時候好易feel到呼吸系統好差 成日抖唔到氣<br />\n（事實上冇幾多有跑步習慣既人會食煙）<br />\n所以佢後尾決心戒<br />\n<br />\n試下將任何一樣運動作為興趣<br />\n可能會有恆心去戒煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d88e27c5a7fec69c4ae40ab5e447e681998f6c46","tid":124782,"uid":75087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T11:53:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我有個同事迷上跑馬拉松、玩三項鐵人賽<br />\n佢練跑既時候好易feel到呼吸系統好差 成日抖唔到氣<br />\n（事實上冇幾多有跑步習慣既人會食煙）<br />\n所以佢後尾決心戒<br />\n<br />\n試下將任何一樣運動作為興趣<br />\n可能會有恆心去戒煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係上個禮拜跑完半馬嘅煙剷，不過係電子煙，食真煙真係無乜可能跑得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}